{"tid":2408844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"仰光飛航情報區有限度運作 中緬突然有運海鮮航班","createTime":"2021-02-15T09:54:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T14:45:11.000Z","uid":68125,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"a64c9f7e402f14abaa16139a86bdb3091dd0b864","tid":2408844,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:54:22.000Z","msg":"以下內容轉自K&rsquo;s Aviation <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1514319515437611/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F495667450636161%2Fposts%2F1514319515437611%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=lQL0ZJWU6LWL4dZDafr4eR0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=c5a4cbc8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/495667450636161/posts/1514319515437611/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EhbcpFD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEhbcpFD.jpg&h=3f1d15db&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1M6zC0E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1M6zC0E.png&h=3903c1ba&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XZKA6T0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXZKA6T0.png&h=960d5c93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前都提及過航空本質就是政治，現時緬甸處於軍事政變，除民用互聯網中斷之外，領空狀況有異常之餘，國家航空公司都有異常情況發生。<br />\n<br />\n綜合緬甸當地傳媒消息及緬甸民航局給飛行員通知 (NOTAM) 資料，仰光國際機場 (RGN) 於1/2起停止辦理業務直至四月底，不過當局已經於3/2宣布仰光國際機場 (RGN) 再次開放。另一方面根據當地消息估計，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">現時有70％的航空交通管制及80％的航空情報服務員工正在罷工</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n現時緬甸當局只准已獲當局批准的國際航班飛越仰光國際機場 (RGN) ，對於飛越仰光飛航情報區的國際航班安排方面，由於航空交通管制人員缺勤，<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">飛越仰光飛航情報區的國際航班除了只准通過特定的航路點外，也需要使用特定空中航線及飛行高度，同時遵守15分鐘間隔規定</span></span>。安排暫定28/2止，但視乎政治環境而決定延長或完結。<br />\n<br />\n於今日民用互聯網中斷後，緬甸國際航空 (8M) 忽然有幾班非表列航班出現，分別為8M791<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">由仰光國際機場 (RGN) 往昆明長水國際機場 (KMG)</span></span>、8M792回程、8M770 由仰光國際機場 (RGN) 往昆明長水國際機場 (KMG)、8M771回程、8M772由仰光國際機場 (RGN) 往昆明長水國際機場 (KMG) 、8M773回程、8M774由仰光國際機場 (RGN) 往昆明長水國際機場 (KMG) 、8M775回程，使用航空器分別為XY-AGV、XY-ALJ，發生時間為當地時間14/2 21:22至15/2 13:43之間。<br />\n<br />\n基於飛行時有曾經關閉過廣播式自動回報監視，所以時間只屬參考。另外有指該等航班為運載海鮮，但是是否運載海鮮就留給大家定奪。"},{"pid":"bd983d4a36f8ebf869fa478eb0cf059ae6e94867","tid":2408844,"uid":61032,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:56:43.000Z","msg":"邊撚度咁多海鮮，都唔知係咪偷運武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0f4e2b3afffe6ac25e0d26654a20cb34cfa253","tid":2408844,"uid":18477,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:57:34.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">搵鬼信係海鮮咩</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff7a5f4ed00bf1b7b9417beb69d6bab425294a2","tid":2408844,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd983d4a36f8ebf869fa478eb0cf059ae6e94867","tid":2408844,"uid":61032,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:56:43.000Z","msg":"邊撚度咁多海鮮，都唔知係咪偷運武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:57:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb77e59f242fd656dbbf3daaf11b95dd9db546ea","tid":2408844,"uid":188176,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bd983d4a36f8ebf869fa478eb0cf059ae6e94867","tid":2408844,"uid":61032,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-15T09:56:43.000Z","msg":"邊撚度咁多海鮮，都唔知係咪偷運武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\